{"title":"Government response to the annual report on the operation of the terrorism acts in 2014","public_updated_at":"2016-11-08T11:07:37Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In September 2015, David Anderson QC, Independent Reviewer of Terrorism Legislation, published his <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-terrorism-acts-in-2014\">annual report on the operation of the terrorism acts in 2014</a>.</p>\n\n<p>This government response addresses the following topics that were covered in the report:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the threat picture</li>\n  <li>the government, law enforcement and security and intelligence agency response</li>\n  <li>proscribed organisations</li>\n  <li>stop and search</li>\n  <li>port and border controls</li>\n  <li>arrest and detention</li>\n  <li>criminal proceedings</li>\n  <li>definition of terrorism</li>\n  <li>the future of the independent reviewer</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-11-08T11:07:37.000+00:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1799113\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/566021/government-response-to-operation-of-terrorism-acts-report-2014-web.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/566021/thumbnail_government-response-to-operation-of-terrorism-acts-report-2014-web.pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a aria-describedby=\"attachment-1799113-accessibility-help\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/566021/government-response-to-operation-of-terrorism-acts-report-2014-web.pdf\">Response to the annual report on the operation of the terrorism acts in 2014 (web)</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"references\">\n          Ref: ISBN <span class=\"isbn\">